data.description: This extraordinary 5-bed, 3-bath home offers a serene atmosphere and a versatile floor plan. The main level showcases hardwood floors, an open layout, and abundant natural light. The expansive living room seamlessly connects to the dining and kitchen areas, with direct access to a wonderfully private balcony, perfect for both starting and ending your day surrounded by greenery. Ideal for entertaining, this level also features the Master suite, two additional bedrooms, and a full hall bath.    The lower level provides flexibility with zoned heating, featuring a spacious family room with a charming fireplace, two large bedrooms, a full bath, and a generous laundry room. The bedrooms on this level offer endless possibilities such as a playroom, office, gym, or a personalized retreat. With a one-car integral garage and outdoor parking for three, the tranquil backyard oasis boasts a level yard, a spacious deck, a serene creek, and a storage shed with ample space.
